<p class="govuk-body">
Log 1234 23/09/2023 was a call made to the police regarding an alleged assault on ******* Street, Blackford, outside the victim's home address. At the time the victim was drinking in the street with the suspect ********, ******* and the victim's partner's **********.
</p>
<p class="govuk-body">
It is alleged that 'out of nowhere' Defendant had attacked the victim by pushing him in the chest, dragging him to the floor by his t-shirt and kicking and stamping on his head over 15 times. Defendant had also climbed onto the fence gate and had jumped onto victim. Defendant has reportedly been saying "COME ON BIG LAD GET UP. YOU'RE NOT DOING ANYTHING NOW ARE YOU" and "THAT'S BEEN COMING A LONG TIME".
</p>
<p class="govuk-body">
Witness 2 from Anywhere has witnessed the assault from her home address and called the police at 20:47hrs. Witness 2 has provided a statement in which she states that she has heard shouting coming from her street "I'M NOT FINISHED WITH YOU YET". As she has looked out her window, she has seen a male (believed to be Defendant) who she knows by the name SINBAD kicking and punching Victim around 5 times. Witness 2 has witnessed Victim fall to the floor and 'SINBAD' continues to punch and kick him, kicking and stamping on his head whilst Victim is on the floor. Witness 2 has then contacted the police.
</p>
<p class="govuk-body">
Witness has provided a statement in which she states that she has been drinking with Victim and 'SINBAD' outside of Victim's address. Witness says that "OUT OF NOWHERE" 'SINBAD' has gotten up and approached Victim from behind, pushing him. 'SINBAD' has then dragged Victim to the floor and has kicked and stamped on Victim's head around 15 times.
</p>
<p class="govuk-body">
Witness has then hit the suspect twice in the head with a cup she has had in her hand to stop 'SINBAD'. 'SINBAD' has then turned around and hit Witness with the back of his hand causing Witness to fall to the floor. Witness states that 'SINBAD' has told her "LOOK WHAT I'M DOING TO YOUR BOYFRIEND". 'SINBAD' has then continued to kick and stamp on Victim's head.
